@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### List categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories?limit=10

### Create category (admin required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Category {{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "Created via REST Client"
}

### Update category (replace :id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete category (replace :id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}

